{"tid":1884654,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（統計）大家一日沖幾多次涼?","createTime":"2020-02-17T17:45:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T19:10:52.000Z","uid":185220,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ecefea2664fad45d0c0fc8081e2187da1d778a55","tid":1884654,"uid":185220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T17:45:43.000Z","msg":"家陣一出完街/放工返到屋企<br />\n都要淋一淋身<br />\n因為唔想頭髮呀嗰d掂到嘅細菌病毒hi到家居環境周圍都係<br />\n但之後煮完飯洗完碗吸埋塵做完家務<br />\n個人又污糟曬又要臨上床前再沖一次<br />\n同另一半搞完又要再沖先訓<br />\n咁都已經一日沖三次<br />\n有啲人如果朝早出門前慣咗淋一淋先出去<br />\n咁即係四次<br />\n<br />\n想統計一下大家一日又會沖幾多次<br />\n習慣係點樣?"},{"pid":"ee175da5822737254b28f200e83e701da2787596","tid":1884654,"uid":5883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T17:50:55.000Z","msg":"試過有年夏日好熱一日沖左6次涼，之後比老母屌到飛天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86cbc72bbeeff2e862886633e6ff677cdd151a1","tid":1884654,"uid":185220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee175da5822737254b28f200e83e701da2787596","tid":1884654,"uid":5883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T17:50:55.000Z","msg":"試過有年夏日好熱一日沖左6次涼，之後比老母屌到飛天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T18:06:42.000Z","msg":"因咩事要鬧你<br />\n嘥水?"},{"pid":"161fb0ac9dc378e98077030c33664c4d410c9fbf","tid":1884654,"uid":3539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T18:07:24.000Z","msg":"平時一日一次 <br />\n如果嗰日朝早做完運動就會沖多次"},{"pid":"5725f302e9c140e5082e145eabb8c84aaa1072b8","tid":1884654,"uid":185220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"161fb0ac9dc378e98077030c33664c4d410c9fbf","tid":1884654,"uid":3539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T18:07:24.000Z","msg":"平時一日一次 <br />\n如果嗰日朝早做完運動就會沖多次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T18:08:23.000Z","msg":"所以一返到屋企唔會沖<br />\n臨訓先沖?"},{"pid":"b309981edd5fcba7d2678bff0e8d97b4c2c9ff5d","tid":1884654,"uid":5883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc